{"tid":1429354,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"夢到福建幫消息","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:00:35.000Z","uid":227803,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7eeb24befde04d0f5e2ca48893ab3d7d5638f9","tid":1429354,"uid":227803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"我朋友發夢夢見<br />\n<br />\n名稱 ： 某哥<br />\n出身：福建<br />\n職業：地盤學徒 <br />\n由於小熊維尼 出錢買起左條村其中一座山 （而家已退休）<br />\n佢本人聲稱 呢幾日福建幫（可能）會有行動<br />\n$1500一位<br />\n已有大量福建人認頭<br />\n佢本人正等待電話準備行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2qoXjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2qoXjx.jpg&h=4631d1d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6349bf270e411215356af44c5c46f41a6091afc8","tid":1429354,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:15:11.000Z","msg":"黎呀仆街，同大陸閪死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老母臭西"},{"pid":"978991ad19e2c04deea4e608e9dd339ca444824a","tid":1429354,"uid":227803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KkgGJ2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkgGJ2u.jpg&h=7c53741b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCaz32u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCaz32u.jpg&h=f3fcf01e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20803e3211f15a87b244cbed8b5588da3d647948","tid":1429354,"uid":80,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"支持福建獨立"},{"pid":"84f82eba59f1a6f2b496bc08d707ac57cfe4281e","tid":1429354,"uid":227803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0385ea7ab7552ac1f2ced3d0c690769f65c6cab","tid":1429354,"uid":227803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f12d2f4ca45571526e825d9d7bcea0fe9993c003","tid":1429354,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e9f3b9fb0b498c748ecafbe2008cc50983fa4b41","tid":1429354,"uid":179649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"元朗都3000蚊位啦，屌<br />\n食水深撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6bb15621b15d84d97a9ccbbc303413ddf83bc8","tid":1429354,"uid":227803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}